James Donlan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/James_Donlan 0 James Donlan (July 23, 1888 – June 7, 1938) was an American actor. Born in San Francisco, California, Donlan appeared in 107 films between 1929 and 1939. He died in Hollywood, California, aged 49, from a heart attack. His daughter is actress Yolande Donlan.
